<div class="content">
	<p>Once you have created a chat session and at least one connection has accepted your chat invitation, you can send direct messages. </p>

	<ol>
		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>Sending Direct Messages</h2>
			<p>To send a messsage, simply type in your message in the content area labelled "What's Up?".  When you're ready to send your message, hit the "Send" button. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-messages/sending-messages/new-message.png" />
				<div class="caption">Sending a Direct Message</div>
			</div>
		</li>

		<li>
			<h2><i class="fa fa-grin"></i>Adding Emoji</h2>
			<p>To add an emoji to your message, click on the first button underneath the message box. Note: emoji will look slightly different depending upon the platform / operating system that you are on. </p>

			<div class="figure">
				<img src="images/help/sharing-messages/sending-messages/adding-emoji.png" />
				<div class="caption">Adding Emoji</div>
			</div>
		</li>
	</ol>
</div>